# Testing Standards

- NEVER break the build.
- You must write or update tests alongside any new component in the same directory (e.g., `component-name.test.tsx`).
- We use `vitest` and `@testing-library/react` for fast headless testing.
- Always run `pnpm test` locally to ensure you haven't introduced regressions before concluding a task.
